summary: This is a brief email or message log from December 30, 2019, indicating that a message was left with a receptionist for an Assistant U.S. Attorney in the Southern District of New York regarding the Epstein case. It serves as a record of attempted contact with the prosecution team.
keyFacts: A message regarding the Epstein case was left for an Assistant U.S. Attorney in the Southern District of New York on December 30, 2019.
The message was left with a receptionist, indicating an attempt to contact the prosecution team.
The document is a record of this attempted communication, dated after Jeffrey Epstein's death in August 2019.
